%% Teacher-owned bounded session (server authority).
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Drafted
    Drafted --> Live: start_session
    Live --> Locked: lock_joins
    Locked --> Live: unlock_joins
    Live --> Closing: end_session
    Locked --> Closing: end_session
    Closing --> Closed: drain_complete
    Closed --> Aggregating: begin_aggregate
    Aggregating --> SyncedToTeacher: persist_roster_stats
    Aggregating --> SyncFailed: persist_error
    SyncFailed --> Aggregating: retry_policy
    SyncedToTeacher --> [*]
